ROS

Interface RosBridgeListener

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    InspectionResult, QuicabotAbout, QuicabotAppCompatActivity, QuicabotControllerMode, QuicabotGenerateReportSetting, QuicabotInspectionLogPage, QuicabotInspectionMode, QuicabotInspectionResult, QuicabotLogin, QuicabotMainPage, QuicabotMapPage, QuicabotPointCloudPage

    public interface RosBridgeListener
    This is a listener interface that all Android Cctivity classes should implement as long as it want to receive message with Rosbridge.

      • onMessage

        Parameters:
        message - the raw string of the entire message
        msgRaw - The processed message string containing op infomation and it helps to tell whether the message is a service or topic
